Source: qdk
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 11)
Maintainer: QNAP QDK <qdk@qnap.com>
Standards-Version: 4.1.4

Package: qdk
Architecture: amd64 arm64 armhf
Depends: python (<< 3.0),
    python (>= 2.7),
    pv,
    xz-utils,
    rsync,
    bsdmainutils,
    gnupg2,
    curl,
    openssl,
    ${shlibs:Depends},
    ${misc:Depends}
Description: QNAP Development Toolkit
 Provides tools to build QNAP packages.
